data.description: Welcome to this 3-Bedroom, 2-Bath POOL HOME in Pine Lake Estates - Large CORNER LOT with NO HOA, Fully Fenced Backyard! New Roof (2019), New Flooring, New Exterior Paint, Fully Replumbed, Irrigation System & SOLAR HEATED POOL. Open Floorplan with Vaulted Ceilings and Wood-Look Tile Throughout Creating a Spacious, Airy Atmosphere. The Master Bedroom Includes an EnSuite Bath, Dual Closets & Private Access to the Pool Area. 2 Add’l Generously Sized Bedrooms with Full Guest Bath. The Heart of this Home is the Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Tile Backsplash, and a Counter-Height Breakfast Bar Overlooking the Dining Room. The Dining Room Features a Vaulted Ceiling with Decorative Wood Beams - Even Includes the Custom Dining Room Table! The Florida Room has Knotty Pine Walls and Tile Flooring - Making a Perfect Space for Entertaining. The Outdoors Features a Large SOLAR HEATED POOL with Loads of Deck Space, both Inside and Out of the Screen Enclosure. Attached 2-Car Garage with an Add’l Parking Allows for Plenty of Parking for Vehicles, Guests & Toys. As An Added Bonus - Check Out the 10x14 COOK SHED with 2 Lofts - Great for Storage, A Shop, She-Shed or Office! Located in Pine lake Estates, You’ll Experience the Best of Both Worlds - A Peaceful Suburban Setting While Still Being Close to All The Amenities and Conveniences St. Cloud Has to Offer. No HOA or CDD Fees, Not in a floodzone. Convenient to the FL Turnpike Entrance, Hwy 192, Schools, Shopping, Restaurants & More!
